data.description: This 1800+ sq ft home sits on a private 3/4 acre lot. The lot is partially wooded with beautiful mature trees. The mobile home itself is a 2016 Clayton that has been upgraded with new carpet, paint and fixtures throughout. Brand new HVAC system still under warranty. Conveniently located 10 minutes from downtown Easley, 5 minutes to downtown Pickens and less than 30 minutes to downtown Greenville.
